dumps(data) ==> This is used convert Python object to json string

loads(data) => Convert Json to python object

Serializars : convert complex data type to Python datatypes

Deserializers : convert Python data to Complex datatypes


Complex datatypes --(seriali..)--> Python native datatypes -(render)--> Json data

JSONRenderer : used to render serializd data into JSON data

Safe = False : can work with any serializer object

JsonResponse(data(should be dict type), safe)

If u use 'POST' method then define create() method in serializer class

